DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

97-2185. Disciplinary Counsel v. Maxwell.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that David Clay Maxwell, Attorney Registration No. 0039122, last known business address in Newark, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of August 12, 1998, to wit: failure to surrender his attorney registration card on or before September 11,1998.
